                <p style="margin-bottom:5px;">Krupa Build Gallery is Founded by Mr. Prakash Magnani in the year of 2016.Over the course of its journey, this business has established a firm foothold in its industry. </p>
                <p style="margin-bottom:5px;">The belief that customer satisfaction is as important as their products and services. They have helped this establishment garner a vast base of customers, which continues to grow day by day. The employees in Krupa Build Gallery are dedicated towards their respective roles and they give a lot of effort to achieve the common vision and larger goals of the company. In the near future, this business aims to expand its line of products and services and cater to a larger client base. The company Occupies a Dealership in Hardware Materials, Building Materials, Electronics & Electrical Products.</p>
                <p style="margin-bottom:5px;">As of 1st July 2020 Krupa Build Gallery has Started a new journey of Online Business namely <b>"Shopping & Saving"</b>, it has a wide range of Products. We offer you convenience of shopping everything that you need for your home - Be It Fresh Fruits & Vegetables, Pulses, Oil, Packaged Food, Dairy Products, Frozen Items ,Other Grocery Products, household cleaning items, personal care products, BuildingMaterials, HardwareProducts, Tiles&Sanitary, Water Tanks & Many more products from a single virtual store.This all products are available on Android app <b>"Shopping & Saving"</b>. Right now, our services are available only in Godhra,further we will go ahead to Grow our business.</p>
                <p style="margin-bottom:5px;">The employees at Krupa Build Gallery are courteous and prompt at providing any assistance. They readily answer any queries or questions that customers may have.</p>
