                <p style="margin-bottom:5px;">Mr. Prakash Magnani, Managing Director- A successful administrator with the modern methods of marketing management. He created Krupa Build Gallery as a brand and plays major role of its growth. His core competency lies in Land Acquisition.  He has proven himself to be a technocrat, playing a key role in construction framework of various projects and its procurement. Supervising the sales department and attaching quality benchmarks to make Krupa a bigger brand.</p>
                <p style="margin-bottom:5px;">He was born at the year 1980, With Schooling at the age of 16 he joined his Family Business at Gajanan Traders, the firm is wholesale supplier of Coconuts & Match Sticks. With the family business he has done so many types of side businesses like book binding work at school, seasonable business of Kites, Retrieval work of Tata Telephone (WLL) &Reliance Communications (WLL) Under subcontractor, Advertisement on Projector at Four Way Location. Since 2009 he started his journey as Real Estate Agent after 1 year with Real Estate Agency, he started a Construction Business in Partnership, from this Industry he got an idea to do something different. So, after 5 years he started a new Journey at Krupa Build Gallery as Founder & Managing Director. Now Krupa Build Gallery is well known firm in the market.</p>
